 knowledge to improve the game further, or even create new games of your own!</p>       <div class="additional_content"><p>University: University of Reading | Subject: N/A | Provider: Future Learn | Instructor: Karsten Ã˜ster Lundqvist</p></div>";s:10:"post_title";s:47:"Begin programming: build your first mobile game";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:132:"Learn the basics of Java programming by developing a simple mobile game that you can run on your computer, Android phone, or tablet.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:57:"begin-programming-build-your-first-mobile-game-2014-02-12";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2014-02-12 19:48:27";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2014-02-12 19:48:27";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:0:"";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:6:"course";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}}